paragraphs.text:
%sql

select * from (select a.*, lead(event_date) over (partition by loyalty_id, session_id order by event_date) as next_event_date from  fact_elements_tab  A  where A.EVENT_DATE  between  to_date('28-OCT-2015') and  to_date('29-OCT-2016') and (A.ELEMENT_ID in ('SUCCESSFUL AUTO LOGIN','SUCCESSFUL LOGIN','SUCCESSFULL LOGIN') or A.ELEMENT_ID like '%OFFER%') and A.SITE_ID in ('NECTARANDROID','NECTARIOS')) where next_evenT_DATE IS NOT NULL

%sql
select a.* from  fact_elements_tab  A  where A.EVENT_DATE  between  to_date('28-OCT-2015') and  to_date('29-OCT-2016') and (A.ELEMENT_ID in ('SUCCESSFUL AUTO LOGIN','SUCCESSFUL LOGIN','SUCCESSFULL LOGIN') or A.ELEMENT_ID like '%OFFER%') and A.SITE_ID in ('NECTARANDROID','NECTARIOS')
